    "client_msg_id": "34d59bd9-5d3f-4054-9238-f92d96d08762",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Up to now I've been thinking:\n\"People can:\n - program spreadsheets\n - or something database-like such as Airtable, MobiDB or MementoDB\n - create little automations on their phones using Tasker, Macrodroid or Automate\n - or use an IFTTT rule\n - make games with Pocket Code, Roblox, Ready Maker, even Minecraft\n - make apps with Sketchware\n\"\nwhich are *very* broad categories to choose to compete with!",
